---
// Scale.astro — Social proof and scale section, built on ZenML
---

<section style="padding: 80px clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px) 100px;">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label" data-reveal>Built to scale</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">Built on the foundation of ZenML.<br>Battle-tested at scale.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">Kitaru is built by the team behind <a href="https://zenml.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="zenml-link">ZenML</a> — the open-source MLOps framework trusted by hundreds of teams to orchestrate production ML pipelines. The same engine that runs thousands of pipelines now powers your agents.</p>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="stats-grid" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">9,000+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">GitHub stars</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">500+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Production teams</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">Millions</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Pipeline runs orchestrated</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-num">3 years</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Production-hardened</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case studies -->
    <div class="proof-grid" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="4">
      <a href="https://zenml.io/case-studies/jetbrains" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="proof-card">
        <div class="proof-company">JetBrains</div>
        <p>Centralized their AI platform on Kubernetes with ZenML's orchestration engine.</p>
        <span class="proof-link">Read case study &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://zenml.io/case-studies/leroy-merlin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="proof-card">
        <div class="proof-company">Leroy Merlin</div>
        <p>Decreased time-to-market from 2 months to 2 weeks with ZenML pipelines.</p>
        <span class="proof-link">Read case study &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://zenml.io/case-studies/brevo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="proof-card">
        <div class="proof-company">Brevo</div>
        <p>Accelerated model development by 80% using ZenML's orchestration layer.</p>
        <span class="proof-link">Read case study &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="zenml-note" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="5">
      Kitaru uses the same checkpoint engine, metadata store, and cloud connectors that power ZenML — now purpose-built for AI agents that need to run for hours, survive crashes, and scale to thousands of concurrent executions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .zenml-link {
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .zenml-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    background: var(--color-card);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-warm);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .proof-card {
    padding: 28px 24px;
    background: var(--color-card);
    transition: background 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .proof-card:hover {
    background: var(--color-elevated);
  }

  .proof-company {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-warm);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .proof-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-dim);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .proof-link {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .zenml-note {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
